::Spears::

Her internal circuits were being repaired inthe chamber, but the 
program war insid her was still raging.  The Trainer chip was being 
forsed back by the maximal chip, but the maximal chip couldn't push 
out the trainer chips programming completely. the two main programs 
fought head to head and were in a tie as far as trying to push the 
other program out.  She was now dealing with two very strong programs.

She groaned a little inside the chamber and started to wake up.  She 
started to feel like her old self again.  her old Maximal self.  She 
opened her eyes smiled. She knocked lightly on the CR door. "Hello? 
Can I get out now? I think I'm ok now.  Hello?"
